dismissalText.commentary: Ed Rainsford lbw b Abdur Razzak 1 (3b 0x4 0x6 5m) SR: 33.33

commentTextItems.html: fraction short on the stumps, went straight on, batsman tries to work it away onside, misses and ball strikes the pads, caught plumb in front, Razzak picks his 1st 5-wicket haul

commentPostTextItems.html: Bangladesh have won the 5-ODI series with 2 more matches to go. Zimbabweans performed better this time but they did not push the runrate and lost their way when they should have gone for some big shots. Razzak ended up with his first 5-wicket haul in his carreer and has been adjudged Man-of-Match. Please join us for the next ODI to be played at Mirpur on Dec 8. Cheers and bye!
